"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"We’re all gonna make it. \\n\\nStep 1: talk about current adoption and that its hard to learn.\\n\\nStep 2: Help happens, but often in unstructured ways on Twitter, Discord or elsewhere. Talk about crypto-natives having the inability to help others unless they have distribution or maybe relies on good intentions?\\n\\nWe’ve seen people create networks by staking (or lending) their electricity, money, disk space, or processing power - why cant we do the same with knowledge?\\n\\nWeb3 fixes this. Introducing HelpDesk, a web3 platform\\n\\nWagmi fam. 2021 was an incredible year for web3 adoption as NFTs and DeFi brought in millions of users into the ecosystem. But if we step back, we are still SO EARLY in the adoption phase. By any calculation, less than 10% (prob closer to 5%) of the world’s population use crypto (FIX). A key pillar of web3 is inclusivity and broadening ownership for everybody with communities and magic Internet money. We need to grow the pie of users.\\n\\nThink about what got you into crypto?\\n\\nThat is why I’m excited to publicly share for the first time what I’ve been building over the past couple months: HelpDesk. HelpDesk\\n\\nTalk about how current business models\\n\\nBy any \\n\\nHow can you help?\\n\\n* Sign up for waitlist (if ur a user)\\n* Join our discord \\n* if you’re a dev/marketer/builder, DM me.\\n\\n[https://twitter.com/RaoulGMI/status/1392939136689053699/photo/1](https://twitter.com/RaoulGMI/status/1392939136689053699/photo/1)\\n\\nTalk about the extra nudge \\n\\nlack of access for many\\n\\nhard to learn on your own (curation sucks, not sure who to trust)\\n\\nOf course, we’re building this in a web3-native way. Kinda meta huh?\\n\\nTalk about users as well as crypto-natives who don’t have the platform to help. \\n\\nWeb3 can make learning models work the way that was difficult before.\\n\\nInstead of upvotes and badges, earn tokens and NFTs.\\n\\nFAQ\\n\\nHow does web3 make this special\",\"timestamp\":1641176499,\"title\":\"Introducing HelpDesk: Making Web3 accessible for everyone\"},\"digest\":\"la_-qDWoLdr7QlnfkkPNYhKUG4p_fFAB_IRlm1hza1o\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xD2035514E8d8389E2d8Ac80113467a3FF1E01D08\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"hV52AxbMPbHK3z9xRwis4nK4fVfcP1xbizFeYfSZ8hQ\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"RMeiVoBSaJih7fhumHD44adFLJIjbiZ1ZwmWk81bj1k\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"GruuNE7dzqiUVfDV6SWqZEq0TDbQXdQMY9sLywETeKvhX7WyrCOu1nDcFy5nY59lUYvtlsAmNpkzPTUWp6wqmw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x919275f955986d37125c1d29935371adc0f47a21a4c9fe9aaf0b4070160d21b878ca74b0c761412b50e5db78b759a1d6f2fd605d0682682c3de445cc6b4afa1d1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"hV52AxbMPbHK3z9xRwis4nK4fVfcP1xbizFeYfSZ8hQ\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"RMeiVoBSaJih7fhumHD44adFLJIjbiZ1ZwmWk81bj1k\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"2CACO_UXjfSr81YFuvcjKLYywNk4E2jdc3sDLLXxU1Q\"}"